body_html:
My best guess is some kind of version skew, similar to the suggestion for #5639. @petewarden might be the best person for advice, but he's very over-burdened with requests at the moment.

Your immediate problem is a node name not being in the op_dict. If I were debugging for myself, I'd try to figure out whether it's just this one node missing, or maybe you somehow failed to get all of the definitions for the graph you're trying to restore.
